    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-0.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "I met Alex when I was 17 years old.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.657,
        "duration": 2.657,
        "sentenceIndex": 0
      },
      {
        "text": "We were at a school event, but I thought he was annoying.",
        "startTime": 2.657,
        "endTime": 7.134,
        "duration": 4.477,
        "sentenceIndex": 1
      },
      {
        "text": "He came late and made jokes all the time.",
        "startTime": 7.134,
        "endTime": 10.246,
        "duration": 3.112,
        "sentenceIndex": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "But something about him makes me smile.",
        "startTime": 10.246,
        "endTime": 13.206,
        "duration": 2.96,
        "sentenceIndex": 3
      },
      {
        "text": "A few months later, we talked more and became friends.",
        "startTime": 13.206,
        "endTime": 17.456,
        "duration": 4.249,
        "sentenceIndex": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "We became friends and shared many happy moments together.",
        "startTime": 17.456,
        "endTime": 21.782,
        "duration": 4.327,
        "sentenceIndex": 5
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.782336,
    "measuredDuration": 21.782336
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b1",
    "bundleIndex": 1,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-1.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-1.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "One day, I saw I had feelings for him.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.126,
        "duration": 3.126,
        "sentenceIndex": 6
      },
      {
        "text": "Maya has real feelings and she shows them to Alex.",
        "startTime": 3.126,
        "endTime": 7.041,
        "duration": 3.916,
        "sentenceIndex": 7
      },
      {
        "text": "The kind that makes your heart race is exciting and fun.",
        "startTime": 7.041,
        "endTime": 11.427,
        "duration": 4.385,
        "sentenceIndex": 8
      },
      {
        "text": "There was a problem, but they found a solution.",
        "startTime": 11.427,
        "endTime": 15.258,
        "duration": 3.831,
        "sentenceIndex": 9
      },
      {
        "text": "This is a big problem for Maya and Alex.",
        "startTime": 15.258,
        "endTime": 18.39,
        "duration": 3.132,
        "sentenceIndex": 10
      },
      {
        "text": "My family has rules and we follow them.",
        "startTime": 18.39,
        "endTime": 21.444,
        "duration": 3.054,
        "sentenceIndex": 11
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.444286,
    "measuredDuration": 21.444286
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b2",
    "bundleIndex": 2,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-2.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "The rules are strict and everyone must follow them.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.619,
        "duration": 3.619,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "Rules said I could not date someone from a different culture.",
        "startTime": 3.619,
        "endTime": 7.948,
        "duration": 4.329,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "My parents told me this when I was a child.",
        "startTime": 7.948,
        "endTime": 10.999,
        "duration": 3.051,
        "sentenceIndex": 14
      },
      {
        "text": "They said not to bring someone like that into our family.",
        "startTime": 10.999,
        "endTime": 15.044,
        "duration": 4.045,
        "sentenceIndex": 15
      },
      {
        "text": "Alex is different from me and it brings shame.",
        "startTime": 15.044,
        "endTime": 18.308,
        "duration": 3.264,
        "sentenceIndex": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "His family comes from another country.",
        "startTime": 18.308,
        "endTime": 21.005,
        "duration": 2.697,
        "sentenceIndex": 17
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 21.004671,
    "measuredDuration": 21.004671
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b3",
    "bundleIndex": 3,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-3.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-3.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "His skin is a different color than mine.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 2.961,
        "duration": 2.961,
        "sentenceIndex": 18
      },
      {
        "text": "His religion is different from others.",
        "startTime": 2.961,
        "endTime": 5.773,
        "duration": 2.813,
        "sentenceIndex": 19
      },
      {
        "text": "My family thinks everything about him is wrong.",
        "startTime": 5.773,
        "endTime": 9.252,
        "duration": 3.479,
        "sentenceIndex": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "Everything about him feels good to me.",
        "startTime": 9.252,
        "endTime": 12.064,
        "duration": 2.813,
        "sentenceIndex": 21
      },
      {
        "text": "We started to date quietly and kept it a secret.",
        "startTime": 12.064,
        "endTime": 15.617,
        "duration": 3.553,
        "sentenceIndex": 22
      },
      {
        "text": "I could not tell anyone about it.",
        "startTime": 15.617,
        "endTime": 18.06,
        "duration": 2.443,
        "sentenceIndex": 23
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 18.059728,
    "measuredDuration": 18.059728
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b4",
    "bundleIndex": 4,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-4.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-4.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "They are not my parents.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 1.593,
        "duration": 1.593,
        "sentenceIndex": 24
      },
      {
        "text": "They are not my grandparents.",
