        "endTime": 3.518,
        "duration": 1.925,
        "sentenceIndex": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "Not even my best friends help me.",
        "startTime": 3.518,
        "endTime": 5.709,
        "duration": 2.191,
        "sentenceIndex": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "I was scared when they found out my secret.",
        "startTime": 5.709,
        "endTime": 8.564,
        "duration": 2.855,
        "sentenceIndex": 27
      },
      {
        "text": "At school, we acted like we were just friends.",
        "startTime": 8.564,
        "endTime": 11.767,
        "duration": 3.204,
        "sentenceIndex": 28
      },
      {
        "text": "We never hold hands in public and feel shy.",
        "startTime": 11.767,
        "endTime": 14.622,
        "duration": 2.855,
        "sentenceIndex": 29
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 14.621927,
    "measuredDuration": 14.621927
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b5",
    "bundleIndex": 5,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "We never sat together at lunch and felt lonely.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.72,
        "duration": 3.72,
        "sentenceIndex": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "We never showed that we were together and happy.",
        "startTime": 3.72,
        "endTime": 7.52,
        "duration": 3.8,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "Living this double life is very tiring for me.",
        "startTime": 7.52,
        "endTime": 11.161,
        "duration": 3.641,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "The stress made me feel very bad and tired.",
        "startTime": 11.161,
        "endTime": 14.565,
        "duration": 3.404,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "I could not sleep at all last night.",
        "startTime": 14.565,
        "endTime": 17.415,
        "duration": 2.85,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "I felt sick every day and it was hard.",
        "startTime": 17.415,
        "endTime": 20.423,
        "duration": 3.008,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 20.422834,
    "measuredDuration": 20.422834
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b6",
    "bundleIndex": 6,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "I lied to everyone I loved and felt very guilty.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 3.474,
        "duration": 3.474,
        "sentenceIndex": 36
      },
      {
        "text": "But I could not stop doing it.",
        "startTime": 3.474,
        "endTime": 5.645,
        "duration": 2.171,
        "sentenceIndex": 37
      },
      {
        "text": "I could not let him go.",
        "startTime": 5.645,
        "endTime": 7.31,
        "duration": 1.665,
        "sentenceIndex": 38
      },
      {
        "text": "After six months, I told my best friend, Maya.",
        "startTime": 7.31,
        "endTime": 10.939,
        "duration": 3.629,
        "sentenceIndex": 39
      },
      {
        "text": "I thought she would understand me but she did not.",
        "startTime": 10.939,
        "endTime": 14.558,
        "duration": 3.619,
        "sentenceIndex": 40
      },
      {
        "text": "But she did not do it.",
        "startTime": 14.558,
        "endTime": 16.15,
        "duration": 1.592,
        "sentenceIndex": 41
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 16.150249,
    "measuredDuration": 16.150249
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b7",
    "bundleIndex": 7,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-7.mp3",
    "audioPath": "romantic-love-1/A1/bundle-7.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
