        "endTime": 10.648,
        "duration": 2.779,
        "sentenceIndex": 80
      },
      {
        "text": "A week later, my father came to see me.",
        "startTime": 10.648,
        "endTime": 13.808,
        "duration": 3.16,
        "sentenceIndex": 81
      },
      {
        "text": "He talked to some work friends from different cultures.",
