        "endTime": 7.997,
        "duration": 2.616,
        "sentenceIndex": 86
      },
      {
        "text": "He wants to meet Alex.",
        "startTime": 7.997,
        "endTime": 9.641,
        "duration": 1.644,
        "sentenceIndex": 87
      },
      {
        "text": "I felt very scared and was terrified.",
        "startTime": 9.641,
        "endTime": 12.407,
        "duration": 2.765,
        "sentenceIndex": 88
      },
      {
        "text": "What happens if they do not like him.",
